INSERT INTO payment_merchants (user_id, sid, secret_key, verified, created_at, updated_at)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, FALSE, NOW(), NOW())
            ON CONFLICT (user_id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                sid = EXCLUDED.sid,
                secret_key = EXCLUDED.secret_key,
                verified = FALSE,
                updated_at = NOW()
